## рџЋЇ Service Breakdown

### 1пёЏвѓЈ API Gateway (Port 4000)
**Role:** Central request router and CORS handler
**Files:**
- `server.js` - Main server file
- `routes/gatewayRoutes.js` - All gateway routes
- `config/gatewayConfig.js` - Configuration

**Key Features:**
- вњ… Routes to all microservices
- вњ… User endpoints forwarding
- вњ… Course endpoints forwarding
- вњ… Enrollment endpoints forwarding
- вњ… Progress endpoints forwarding
- вњ… Certificate endpoints forwarding

### 2пёЏвѓЈ User Service (Port 5000)
**Role:** Authentication and user management
**Files:**
- `userController.js` - Register, login, profile management
- `userModel.js` - User schema with bcrypt
- `userRoutes.js` - Authentication endpoints

**Endpoints:**
- `POST /register` - User registration
- `POST /login` - User login
- `GET /:userId` - User profile
- `PUT /:userId` - Update profile
- `DELETE /:userId` - Delete user

### 3пёЏвѓЈ Course Service (Port 5001)
**Role:** Course creation and management
**Files:**
- `courseController.js` - CRUD operations
- `courseModel.js` - Course schema with modules
- `courseRoutes.js` - Course endpoints

**Endpoints:**
- `GET /all` - List all courses
- `GET /:courseId` - Course details
- `POST /create` - Create course
- `PUT /:courseId` - Update course
- `DELETE /:courseId` - Delete course

### 4пёЏвѓЈ Enrollment Service (Port 5002)
**Role:** Student enrollment management
**Files:**
- `enrollmentController.js` - Enrollment operations
- `enrollmentModel.js` - Enrollment schema
- `enrollmentRoutes.js` - Enrollment endpoints

**Endpoints:**
- `POST /enroll` - Enroll student
- `GET /my-enrollments` - User enrollments
- `PUT /:enrollmentId/status` - Update status
- `DELETE /:enrollmentId/cancel` - Cancel enrollment

### 5пёЏвѓЈ Progress Service (Port 5003)
**Role:** Student progress and analytics
**Files:**
- `progressController.js` - Progress tracking
- `progressModel.js` - Progress schema
- `progressRoutes.js` - Progress endpoints

**Endpoints:**
- `POST /track` - Track lesson completion
- `GET /my-progress` - User progress
- `PUT /:progressId/score` - Update score
- `GET /course/:courseId/stats` - Statistics

### 6пёЏвѓЈ Certificate Service (Port 5004)
**Role:** Certificate generation and verification
**Files:**
- `certificateController.js` - Certificate operations
- `certificateModel.js` - Certificate schema
- `certificateRoutes.js` - Certificate endpoints

**Endpoints:**
- `POST /generate` - Generate certificate
- `GET /my-certificates` - User certificates
- `GET /verify/:certificateNumber` - Verify
- `PUT /:certificateId/revoke` - Revoke

### 7пёЏвѓЈ Frontend (Port 3000)
**Role:** User interface and client
**Files:**
- `App.jsx` - Main app component
- `pages/*` - Page components
- `components/*` - Reusable components
- `services/api.js` - API client

**Pages:**
- Home - Browse courses
- Login - User login
- Register - User registration
- Dashboard - User dashboard
- CourseDetails - Course information

