## рџљЂ Quick Start Guide

### Step 1: Navigate to Project
```bash
cd "d:\Online Course Platform"
```

### Step 2: Read Getting Started Guide
```bash
# Open in editor
GETTING_STARTED.md
```

### Step 3: Install Dependencies
```bash
# Frontend
cd frontend && npm install

# API Gateway
cd ../api-gateway && npm install

# All services
cd ../user-service && npm install
cd ../course-service && npm install
cd ../enrollment-service && npm install
cd ../progress-service && npm install
cd ../certificate-service && npm install
```

### Step 4: Start MongoDB
```bash
mongod
```

### Step 5: Start Each Service (in separate terminals)
```bash
# Terminal 1
cd api-gateway && npm run dev

# Terminal 2
cd user-service && npm run dev

# Terminal 3
cd course-service && npm run dev

# Terminal 4
cd enrollment-service && npm run dev

# Terminal 5
cd progress-service && npm run dev

# Terminal 6
cd certificate-service && npm run dev

# Terminal 7
cd frontend && npm run dev
```

### Step 6: Access Application
```
http://localhost:3000
```

